snippet.title: RaidLand - Official Steam Trailer
snippet.description:
Thank you to everyone who played and enjoyed Raid Land! Unfortunately this game has been archived and is no longer available. We hope you join us on our other fun game https://shellshock.io!


Get the latest Blue Wizard news by joining our Discord community at https://discord.gg/bluewizard

---
RaidLand is a competitive, class-based PvP fantasy RPG! Play as the Hunter, Warrior or Berserker in Team Greed mode ~ Hunt & kill your opponents, steal & hoard gold for victory ~ Level up, unlock skill perks & masteries in each class!
